data.description: OFFERING ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.125% INTEREST!  Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the desirable community of Baywood village.  This home encapsulates the essence of coastal living with unparalleled comfort. As you step inside, natural light pours through the spacious living areas, highlighting the contemporary design and inviting ambiance. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample storage, and a breakfast bar, making it the perfect hub for culinary adventures and gatherings with loved ones.The master suite, complete with a private en-suite bath, creates a private haven for relaxation and rejuvenation. Two additional generously sized bedrooms provide versatility for accommodating guests or setting up a home office. Outside, a meticulously landscaped backyard beckons you to unwind and embrace the coastal breeze while creating lasting memories.  Roof was completed in 2020.  Baywood Village offers an array of community amenities, including a playground and clubhouse adding to the appeal of this already alluring neighborhood. Conveniently located near Tarpon Springs and Dunedin, this home ensures easy access to everyday conveniences.  Don’t miss the opportunity to make this gem your own. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities of creating your own coastal haven in this prime Palm Harbor location.
